      • showStudyDeletePopup

        private boolean showStudyDeletePopup
        Confirmation popup for deleting (working) study versions. -- you can only delete working versions from the ManageStudies page. To destroy an archived copy you have to go to to the StudyPage for that study, we're not supplying buttons for that in the ManageStudies view.
